item.title: CVE-2021-21269|2024-08-03T18:09:14.980Z -- keymaker-mx -- keymaker
item.description: Keymaker is a Mastodon Community Finder based Matrix Community serverlist page Server. In Keymaker before version 0.2.0, the assets endpoint did not check for the extension. The rust `join` method without checking user input might have made it abe to do a Path Traversal attack causing to read more files than allowed. This is fixed in version 0.2.0.
